00:19:11.030 --> 00:19:13.110
Bagaimanakah ibu anda meninggal dunia?

00:19:20.830 --> 00:19:22.550
Jika anda tidak mahu bercakap mengenainya,

00:19:22.550 --> 00:19:23.550
